# Pops Marketing Website Branch Convention

For work scoped to the Pops marketing website in `apps/pops-website/**`, post and push completed changes to the `main` branch unless the user explicitly says otherwise.

Before pushing, pull with rebase from `origin/main` and resolve any conflicts:

```shell
git pull --rebase origin main
git push origin main
```
